data.description: Welcome to 4935 Jupiter Hills Drive!! This stunning home is located in King's Island on a quarter of an acre and is backed up to a community pond! Entering the home you will be welcomed into the foyer that gives you a taste of all the fine details this home has to offer. From the hardwood floors, crown molding with ambient lighting, wide-open living spaces, knotty alder cabinets, and granite countertops, this home will leave you speechless. The main level boasts a light-filled living room with an exterior entrance leading you out to the back deck with exquisite views of your backyard pond! Neighboring the living room you will find the dining area & kitchen. The kitchen features a large breakfast bar that overlooks the main floor living area, tons of cabinets for storage, & a built-in desk. Secluded from the kitchen and living area you will find 2 additional bedrooms, a laundry room, and a full bathroom. The master suite is nothing short of spectacular and features views of the pond! The master bathroom includes a separate garden tub, a shower, and a secluded walk-in closet with plenty of room. The basement features a massive living room, a private theatre room, 3 additional bedrooms, a full bathroom, and an oversized storage room! Don't miss the opportunity to see this home!
